snippet.title: Fallout Season 2 - Official Teaser Trailer | gamescom 2025
snippet.description:
Watch the Season 2 Teaser Trailer for Fallout, the live-action series based on the Bethesda-developed Fallout game series distributed by Amazon MGM Studios, and Kilter Films produced in association with Bethesda Game Studios and Bethesda Softworks.

Fallout is based on one of the most popular video game franchises of all time and is set 200 years after an apocalyptic event. The story follows the gentle denizens of luxury fallout shelters who are forced to return to the irradiated hellscape their ancestors left behind—and are shocked to discover an incredibly complex, gleefully weird, and highly violent universe waiting for them. The brief teaser trailer depicts Lucy MacLean and Cooper Howard venturing off across the wasteland with New Vegas in the distance, calling back to the famous game location in the franchise.

Fallout Season 2 stars Ella Purnell, Aaron Moten, Walton Goggins, Kyle MacLachlan, Moisés Arias, Frances Turner, and more. The Executive Producers for Fallout Season 2 are Jonathan Nolan and Lisa Joy, alongside Geneva Robertson-Dworet and Graham Wagner also serve as executive producers, creators, and showrunners. Todd Howard, Bethesda Game Studios, executive produces along with James Altman for Bethesda Softworks. 

Fallout Season 2 is premiering in December 17, 2025, with the series also being renewed for Season 3.

#IGN #gamescom2025

snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV Official Announce Trailer | Gamescom Opening Night 2025
snippet.description:
At last, back to war! Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV officially revealed during Gamescom Opening Night Live 2025!

Battle for planet Kronus as Warhammer 40,000's ultimate real time strategy game returns, featuring the largest campaign ever with four distinct factions battling it out in epic, brutal large-scale conflicts. 

Dawn of War IV returns to the legendary RTS series’ roots with satisfying gameplay and a brutal, expanded Sync Kill system. Take command of four Warhammer 40,000 factions, including, for the first time in the Dawn of War series, the Adeptus Mechanicus! Fight through 70+ campaign missions solo or with a friend in a story crafted by legendary Black Library author John French. Immerse yourself in endlessly replayable modes including Last Stand and Skirmish, or take the fight to the world with intense multiplayer combat.

Read more on Warhammer Community: https://www.warhammer-community.com/en-gb/articles/l8pdgqps/warhammer-40000-dawn-of-war-iv/

🎤 Song Lyrics: Breathe - Blu Cantrell, ft. Sean Paul

Lyrics : 

[Intro: Sean Paul]
Sean Paul and Blu Cantrell
Remix that gon' make the head swell, yo
Yo, hey, yo, boom, yo, hey, yo, dutty, yeah

[Chorus: Sean Paul & Blu Cantrell]
(Breathe) So what's that supposed to be about, baby?
Gal, free up ya vibe and stop acting crazy
Reminisce 'pon all the good times daily
Why you trying to pose like I be acting shady? (Breathe)
What's that supposed to be about, baby? (Hey, yo)
Gal, free up ya vibe and stop acting crazy
Sean Paul give you the good loving daily
Now you trying to pose like I be acting shady? (Talk to me now, Blu)

[Verse 1: Blu Cantrell]
You say you love me, say you love me
But you're never there for me, yeah (Hmm-mm)
You be crying, slowly dying
When I decide to leave (Oh, oh)

[Pre-Chorus: Blu Cantrell]
All we do is make up (Make up), then break up (Break up)
Why don't we wake up and see?
When love hurts (Love hurts), it won't work (Won’t work)
Maybe we need some time alone
We need to let it breathe
[Chorus: Sean Paul & Blu Cantrell]
So what's that supposed to be about, baby? (Breathe)
Gal, free up ya vibe and stop acting crazy (Breathe)
Reminisce 'pon all the good times daily (Breathe)
Why you trying to pose like I be acting shady?

[Verse 2: Blu Cantrell]
You're only lonely when your homie
Ain't got a ride or no loot, yeah (Yeah), uh-huh
Then comes the drama
Some other girl is claiming she's going out with you (Hmm-mm)

[Pre-Chorus: Blu Cantrell]
All we do is make up (Make up), then break up (Break up)
Why don't we wake up and see?
When love hurts (Love hurts), it won't work (Won’t work)
Maybe we need some time alone
We need to let it breathe

[Chorus: Sean Paul & Blu Cantrell]
So what's that supposed to be about, baby? (Breathe)
Gal, free up ya vibe and stop acting crazy (Breathe)
Shady (Shady), Shady (Breathe, breathe, ooh)

[Verse 3: Sean Paul]
Dutty, yeah
Why, girl (C'mon, girl), for the fourth time
If I make it very clear to you
You're very dear to me
And all my heart me share to you
Me not unfair to you
Woman, I want fa real and make you know
That I will always draw near to you
But me know me nah no fair to you (Eh!)
Me stand up like a man and I'll be there (Okay)
Because I care for you
Long time me a tell you me no have no gal a compare to you
Woman, if you leave me now
I'm gonna shed a lot of tear for you
You want to breathe and still you're not exhaling (Yo, yo)
Say you want to leave 'cause this relationship failing (C'mon, girl)
Ain't nobody say that it would be smooth sailing
Girl, I want to know why you bailing ship, yo
.[Chorus: Sean Paul & Blu Cantrell]
So what's that supposed to be about, baby? (Breathe)
Gal, free up ya vibe and stop acting crazy (Breathe)
Reminisce 'pon all the good times daily (Lady a good girl)
Why you trying to pose like I be acting shady? (Let it breathe)

[Outro: Blu Cantrell & Sean Paul]
(Shady, shady, shady, baby, baby) Baby, we need some time alone
So we can just breathe (Breathe)
Let it breathe (Breathe)
(Breathe) Breathing
(Breathe, breathe) Let it breathe (Breathe)
Breathe (Breathe, breathe), uh-uh-uh
Yeah, let it breathe, yeah (Shady, shady, shady, baby, baby)
Time to breathe, y'all
(Breathe, breathe) Oh, breathe
Time to breathe y'all (Breathe)

snippet.title: "ENDLESS NIGHT" – 99 NIGHTS IN THE FOREST SONG | BloxBoys
snippet.description:

You must survive 99 nights in the forest, where monsters become stronger with every passing night. Gather resources, craft tools, and stay alive as the woods grow darker and more dangerous. Only the strongest will endure all 99. 🌲🦉🔥

#roblox #bloxboysoriginal #gamingmusic #99nightsintheforest #robloxmusic #forestmonsters #robloxhorror #bloxboysoriginal #survivalmusic #nightchallenge #robloxupdate

CREDITS:
Animation ►  @memeycorny7773  
Vocals ► @n3onine
Prod ► @NotiniRBLX

- --- -----Lyrics -- --- --- -- -
Night one, still feeling brave,
Night two, I’m digging my grave.
By night three, I’ve learned the sound
Of footsteps that don’t touch the ground.

Campfire’s low, my hands are numb,
Every shadow asksing me to come.
The trees lean close like they all know
Where I’ll be buried when I go.

Ninety-nine nights, no sunrise here,
No one comes, no help appears.
We run, we hide, we scream, we fight,
Through ninety-nine nights of endless night.

Some kids vanish, some kids stay,
Some kids laugh ‘cause they’ve gone insane.
Whispers in the dark, pulling at my sleeve,
Telling me lies I almost believe.

The deer’s not the only thing out here—
There’s voices, claws and things unclear.
Some nights feel like they never end,
Some nights eat your only friend.

Ninety-nine nights, no sunrise here,
No one comes, no help appears.
We run, we hide, we scream, we fight,
Through ninety-nine nights of endless night.

They say if you make it, you get to leave,
But I don’t trust what they want me to believe.
What if the game just starts again
With new kids trapped where I have been.

Ninety-nine nights, no sunrise here,
No one comes, no help appears.
We run, we hide, we scream, we fight,
Through ninety-nine nights of endless night.
 
Ninety-nine nights, no sunrise here,
No one comes, no help appears.
We run, we hide, we scream, we fight,
Through ninety-nine nights of endless night.
